{"tid":1490472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一日  全球反共大遊行！！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:58:41.000Z","uid":92347,"like":243,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"cc73331d5d26dd415b73f8b1a66300836fd1b331","tid":1490472,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"毛澤東-&quot;凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。&quot; <br />\n<br />\n中共希望順利慶祝中華人民共和國成立70周年，同時要求香港盡快平亂<br />\n我地正正要反對!  不單唔去慶祝，仲要反對!<br />\n<br />\n主題: <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全球反共大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n將中國共產黨，呢個冷血殺人政權，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冠以 極權主義國家之名</span></strong><br />\n以此作為文宣方向，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將香港政府高層視為極權主義國家下之傀儡</span></strong><br />\n向全球文宣! 以香港追求民主自由為出發點，號召全世界同路人，同步係當日舉行集會/遊行! <br />\n<br />\n地點: 當地首都/ 政府總部附近, 香港可以係添馬總部<br />\n<br />\n有此建議，希望有人和應，推到民陣搞!<br />\n推到文宣組幫手!<br />\n有咩意見, 一齊討論!<br />\n<br />\n希望有生之年，可以睇到佢滅亡"},{"pid":"a89909d04350146303b97638120211fc8a7e9824","tid":1490472,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7bdfc6797c85b4fc251a89d9e0054a39e7c380cd","tid":1490472,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"be6189d0c854b38f8f37b982e9f306f6bd84e9d4","tid":1490472,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"484b65206945b94470a6fcfafa8116b19ad147ad","tid":1490472,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54f286be85b3a9ddcb6b318d0df50367083d3e17","tid":1490472,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"推 令佢地70大壽 無面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1e8de4457c8df0c19a2c96603455cf67b14505","tid":1490472,"uid"